name: Willow
description: Please. Show me what you’re thinking. Being miles apart, the distance drives me crazy. All I hope is for you to stay, but I’m stuck in this limbo… floating. I hate this game and I’m reluctant to tell. So, I’d rather turn my head, but I only see you. Helpless, but it just feels so right. I’m dazed in disbelief, but the phosphenes continue to spread within my eyes…
